      "name": "Hemolysis model validation via published literature survey",
      "description": "A comprehensive review of peer-reviewed hemolysis modelling studies was conducted. Published datasets and model comparisons from prior FDA benchmark exercises were collated and compared against predicted RH values from the CFD model. The literature review identified strong concordance between the present model outputs and those reported in comparable pump configurations, supporting the claim that RH predictions are credible for the CPB COU.",
