    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at this model risk level. The literature review provides a strong evidence base for model credibility, and the RH index predictions are within acceptable tolerance relative to published benchmarks. The assessment team concludes that the CFD model is credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
